title: SlaverHylic01Interaction
---
Hylic Slaver: Halt! You are approaching a restricted mining area, hearth of our matriarch, Mother Sibulo. State your purpose.
<<make_contact_with_npc "SlaverHylic01">>
-> I'm here to rescue a Hybrid named Ala'an. Do you know him?
    <<jump YouClaimToBeRescuingAlaan>>
-> I'm here to relinquish my freedom and become a slave.
    <<jump YouClaimedToBeSumbittingForThralldom>>
-> I need to talk to the leader of your operation. Sibulo, was it?
===

title: WishToSubmitToMatriarchForSlavery
---
-> No, uh, I don't. I come at the request of The Diplomat, your fellow Hylic. I am only here for the Hybrid named Ala'an.
    <<jump YouClaimToBeRescuingAlaan>>
-> Exactly yes, I've come to submit to your master for thralldom. 
    <<jump YouClaimedToBeSumbittingForThralldom>>
===

title: YouClaimedToBeSumbittingForThralldom
---
Hylic Slaver: This is irregular. I would not stop you, however, if you indeed wish to be thrall to my master.
-> Ok, then. What now? 
Hylic Slaver: I'm just an enforcer. You'll have to talk to the supervisor. It will likely grant you your wish, with our master's approval.
-> And where are they?
    Hylic Slaver: The mine of course. The one where you wish to work as a thrall. South of here.
-> I'll head there.
===

title: YouClaimToBeRescuingAlaan
---
Hylic Slaver: The Hylic you speak of is known to us. That one adopts no master. Mother Sibulo warns us not to trust it.
Hylic Slaver: The name of the thrall you speak of is one I recognize, but I don't know any details.
Hylic Slaver: You should not trust it either. Am I to take it that you are in league with this traitor?
-> Are you not also an outcast? You speak as though pledging yourself to your Matriarch changes that. (Suggested Willpower: 3)
    <<if get_willpower() < 3>>
        Hylic Slaver: How dare you? Our Zyt is good and just. You will leave us.
    <<else>>
        <<jump SlaverHy01_Passed_Check_WP_01>>
    <<endif>>
-> But I do trust it. It seems to be trying to do right by all in Midsheol. 
    Hylic Slaver: I'm sure it thinks that it is. I warn you, you do not understand our ways, and this 'Diplomat' courts trouble.
    -> Still, I think I want to at least try to help him and Ala'an.
        Hylic Slaver: I'm just an enforcer. I do not decide what thralls may come or go.
        Hylic Slaver: If you must, speak with the Supervisor. I cannot see how it would allow what you ask.
===

title: SlaverHy01_Passed_Check_WP_01
---
Hylic Slaver: You make sense, human, much as I find solace in this parapolity. I'll listen carefully.
    -> Let me speak with your Matriarch. Let her make up her own mind.
        Hylic Slaver: That seems to me acceptable. I will signal to the gatekeeper to expect and admit you.
    -> I would have you bring Ala'an here to work as do these two outside the gate. Then, if he would follow where I lead, him and I would leave.
        Hylic Slaver: I cannot allow this. I thought you were going to talk sense.
===